<div style="font-size: inherit;"><h4 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Role</strong>:</h4><p style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A customer interested in purchasing apparel and accessories online.</p><h4 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Goal</strong>:</h4><p style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">To browse, search, purchase, and manage orders easily on the website.</p><hr style="text-align:start;text-decoration:none"><h3 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Detailed User Journey</h3><ol style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li><strong>Landing Page (Order Tracking Page)</strong>:<ul><li><strong>Action</strong>: The customer enters the<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Order Number</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Email Address</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>to check the status of their order or start a return.</li><li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Simplify post-purchase management for both logged-in users and guests.</li><li><strong>Elements</strong>:<ul><li>Text fields for<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Order Number</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Email Address</strong>.</li><li>A disabled<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Submit</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>button that becomes active when valid inputs are provided.</li><li>A prompt for existing users to log in for a better experience.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ol><hr style="text-align:start;text-decoration:none"><ol start="2" style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li><strong>Shopping/Browsing Page</strong>:<ul><li><strong>Action</strong>: The customer browses categories like Men’s, Women’s, and Kids’ clothing and accessories.</li><li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Enable customers to explore products with clear filters and sorting options.</li><li><strong>Elements</strong>:<ul><li>Sidebar filters:<ul><li><strong>Categories</strong>: Tops, Hoodies, Jackets, Trousers, etc.</li><li><strong>Shop by Price</strong>: Budget-specific filtering.</li><li><strong>Size, Gender, and Color</strong>: For narrowing down preferences.</li><li><strong>Material, Technology, and Features</strong>: Highlight specific product characteristics like "Sustainable Materials."</li></ul></li><li>Main display: Product images, names, prices, and key highlights.</li><li>Sorting feature (e.g., price low to high, new arrivals).</li></ul></li></ul></li></ol><hr style="text-align:start;text-decoration:none"><ol start="3" style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li><strong>Checkout/Delivery Page</strong>:<ul><li><strong>Action</strong>: The customer fills out personal and delivery information and proceeds to payment.</li><li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Ensure seamless order placement and adherence to customs regulations (for India).</li><li><strong>Elements</strong>:<ul><li><strong>Delivery Information</strong>:<ul><li>Name, address, email, phone number.</li><li>Clear notes about customs regulations, ensuring compliance by matching KYC and shipping addresses.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Order Summary</strong>:<ul><li>Item details (name, quantity, price).</li><li>Subtotal and shipping fees.</li><li>Estimated delivery timeline.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Customs Clearance Section</strong>:<ul><li>Prompts for National ID information to facilitate customs processing.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ol><hr style="text-align:start;text-decoration:none"><h3 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Feature Specification for the Website</h3><h4 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>General Features</strong>:</h4><ol style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li><p><strong>Responsive Design</strong>:</p><ul><li>Optimized for desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Navigation</strong>:</p><ul><li>Persistent top navigation bar with links to<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Men</strong>,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Women</strong>,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Kids</strong>,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>New &amp; Featured</strong>, and<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Sales</strong>.</li><li>Search functionality and a quick-access cart icon.</li></ul></li></ol><hr style="text-align:start;text-decoration:none"><h4 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Key Functionalities</strong>:</h4><ol style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li><p><strong>Order Management</strong>:</p><ul><li><strong>Tracking</strong>:<ul><li>Input fields for Order Number and Email Address.</li><li>Authentication for guest and logged-in users.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Returns</strong>:<ul><li>Options to initiate a return from the tracking page.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Product Discovery</strong>:</p><ul><li><strong>Filtering Options</strong>:<ul><li>Wide range of filters for tailoring the shopping experience.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Sorting</strong>:<ul><li>By price, popularity, new arrivals, etc.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Product Details</strong>:<ul><li>High-resolution images, product descriptions, and price breakdowns.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Checkout Process</strong>:</p><ul><li><strong>Delivery Information</strong>:<ul><li>Validations for correct shipping address and customs clearance.</li><li>Notes on customs regulations for specific regions.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Payment Options</strong>:<ul><li>Not visible in the screenshots but should include multiple methods (credit card, net banking, wallet).</li></ul></li><li><strong>Order Summary</strong>:<ul><li>Transparent cost breakdown and delivery estimates.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Account Management</strong>:</p><ul><li><strong>Guest Users</strong>:<ul><li>Can manage orders with minimal details (Order ID, Email).</li></ul></li><li><strong>Logged-in Users</strong>:<ul><li>Access past orders, exclusive offers, and saved addresses.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Accessibility</strong>:</p><ul><li>High contrast UI elements.</li><li>Keyboard and screen reader compatibility.</li></ul></li></ol><br></div>
